        '{\"html\":\"<h3>Gwybodaeth am y Wefan \\/ Website Information<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Mae&rsquo;r anodiadau ar y safle yma&rsquo;n cael eu creu gan y gymuned, a gall fod mwy o waith i&rsquo;w wneud i&rsquo;w cwblhau. Rhybudd &ndash; er bod yr anodiadau i gyd wedi eu harbed, nid oes modd gweld mwy na 10 o anodiadau ar y tro ar hyn o bryd.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Annotations on this site are being created by the community and may need extra work to complete. Warning &ndash; although all annotations have been saved, it is currently only possible to view up to 10 annotations.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Dewiswch Brosiect&nbsp;Cyfrannu Torfol:<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li><a draggable=\\\"false\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.llyfrgell.cymru\\/darganfod\\/oriel-ddigidol\\/archifau\\/cofnodion-tribiwnlysoedd-apel-y-rhyfel-mawr-sir-aberteifi\\/\\\">Cofnodion Tribiwnlysoedd (Ap&ecirc;l) y Rhyfel Mawr Sir Aberteifi - CWBLHAWYD - Chwiliwch y Cofnodion<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><a draggable=\\\"false\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/crowd.library.wales\\/cy\\/s\\/livingstone\\/page\\/home\\\">Casgliad Ffotograffau Gwilym Livingstone Evans<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><a draggable=\\\"false\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/crowd.library.wales\\/cy\\/s\\/livingstone2\\/page\\/home\\\">Casgliad Ffotograffau Gwilym Livingstone Evans 2<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><a draggable=\\\"false\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/crowd.library.wales\\/cy\\/s\\/livingstone3\\/page\\/home\\d\">Casgliad Ffotograffau Gwilym Livingstone Evans 3<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><a draggable=\\\"false\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/crowd.library.wales\\/cy\\/s\\/kyffin\\/page\\/home\\\">Dyddiaduron Kyffin<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><a draggable=\\\"false\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/crowd.library.wales\\/cy\\/s\\/dcharries\\/page\\/home\\\">Portreadau D C Harries<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Please Select a Crowdsourcing Project:<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n\\t<li><a draggable=\\\"false\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.library.wales\\/discover\\